foreignData.name: Cateranischer Sklavenhändler
foreignData.text:
Sumpftarnung
5, {T}: Durchsuche Deine Bibliothek nach einer Söldnerkarte mit umgewandelten Manakosten von 5 oder weniger und bringe diese Karte ins Spiel. Mische danach Deine Bibliothek.

foreignData.name: カテラン組合の奴隷商人

name: Cateran Slaver
originalText:
Swampwalk (This creature is unblockable as long as defending player controls a swamp.)
o5, oc
T: Search your library for a Mercenary card with converted mana cost 5 or less and put that card into play. Then shuffle your library.

rulings.text: Because the “search” requires you to find a card with certain characteristics, you don’t have to find the card if you don’t want to.

text:
Swampwalk (This creature can't be blocked as long as defending player controls a Swamp.)
{5}, {T}: Search your library for a Mercenary permanent card with mana value 5 or less, put it onto the battlefield, then shuffle.
